frames.caption: A majestic bald eagle perches on a rocky outcrop, surveying the mountainous landscape. The eagle's sharp gaze and powerful stance convey a sense of dominance and grace. Snow-dusted peaks and a misty atmosphere create a serene yet dramatic backdrop.
